{%- comment -%}
  Product PDF URL resolver.

  Maps product.handle -> PDF filename stored in theme assets/.
  Uses `asset_url` so PDFs deploy with the theme (no Admin upload needed).

  Usage (from a section/template):
    {%- capture pdf_url -%}{%- render 'product-pdf-url', product: product -%}{%- endcapture -%}

  Outputs a blank string if there is no match.
{%- endcomment -%}

